<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her vicztum, uns
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt <expan>B<ex>erhtold</ex></expan>
                        Deihsler und <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Lawging<ex>er</ex></expan> von iren und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gesellschaft wegen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>hercz<ex>og</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, amptleute etwievil hab und kauffmanschaft
                                <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und gen Walde <add>in das
                            gerihte</add> gefürt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; darümb wir
                                    <add><expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan></add> den
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pilsach<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener,
                        czu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>hercz<ex>og</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, gnaden <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                <add><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen</add>
<expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>hercz<ex>og</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, gnaden <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        günstige hilff und fürdrung beweysen wöllet, daz in <add>dieselb ir hab und
                                    <expan>kauffmansch<ex>aft</ex></expan></add> und on hindernüsse
                        volge <add>und ledig werde</add>, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <app>
<note place="marginleft"> - <expan>ist<ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan>l<ex>itte</ex>re</expan></note>
